cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Aegis: a layered defense for large language models"
abstract: >-
  Aegis is a defense-in-depth system for LLM jailbreak and prompt-injection defense,
  combining de-obfuscation, a fast detector, a fine-tuned guard, agent and tool-injection
  defense, output moderation, and continuous red-teaming, designed to run on a single free
  GPU and aligned to the OWASP LLM Top 10, NIST AI RMF, and MITRE ATLAS.
type: software
authors:
